{"tid":343465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半空遇冰雹　客機整塊擋風玻璃龜裂　機長憑30年經驗安全着陸","createTime":"2017-08-01T12:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T10:01:18.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"475d72a465ad5171c56c480de18a238d1a62a8c3","tid":343465,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">半空遇冰雹　客機整塊擋風玻璃龜裂　機長憑30年經驗安全着陸</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170801/s00005/1ef1b008c59a81aa6851c3c91b124b1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170801%2Fs00005%2F1ef1b008c59a81aa6851c3c91b124b1d.jpg&h=9efcefbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170801/s00005/1ef1b523b91138cb6d746f65d72cec27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170801%2Fs00005%2F1ef1b523b91138cb6d746f65d72cec27.jpg&h=8bc3cc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一架原定由土耳機伊斯坦布爾飛往塞浦路斯的客機，因遇上冰雹，駕駛艙整塊擋風玻璃被擊碎龜裂，自動駕駛系統亦失靈，機師雖然看不到降落位置，但憑着30年飛行經驗仍然最終讓客機安全着陸。飛機在跑道上煞停後，121名乘客掌聲四起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伊斯坦布爾上周四(7月27日)出現冰雹風暴，冰雹有雞蛋般大小，雖然只維持約20分鐘，但卻造成嚴重交通混亂和洪水氾濫。烏克蘭籍機師亞歷山大‧阿科波夫(Alexander Scherba)駕駛的空中巴士A320在伊斯坦布爾機場起飛10分鐘後，整塊擋風玻璃就被冰雹擊裂。<br />\n<br />\n阿科波夫說，他駕駛飛機已有30年，「你看到飛機着陸嗎？還可以吧？乘客都生還。這是正常的，這就是我們專業性的可靠」。<br />\n<br />\n亞歷山大的駕駛技術讓121名乘客和6名機組人員安然無恙，他其後獲烏克蘭總統頒發勳章表揚他的勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n(獨立報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170801/s00005/1501572496140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170801%2Fs00005%2F1501572496140&d=g6HUuDliaoTZmEauGmvtRBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=4193a542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170801%2Fs00005%2F1501572496140&h=aa94ed17\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170801/s00005/1501572496140</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xn5hC7zKruY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXn5hC7zKruY&d=g6HUuDliaoTZmEauGmvtRBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=4ce56ac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xn5hC7zKruY</a>"},{"pid":"6759b8f906e6825d79ed155016557a12ae03dcc3","tid":343465,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"我諗起徒手擋冰雹果位超級巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530d921910c01afbe2c09f3dd8a661021eb0a603","tid":343465,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edfcbf4b4d1aa018d175b246c5ea5b8fba5cba5","tid":343465,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d66c9134baffe857acc78db4fcdc2af8c73a40a","tid":343465,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有自動導航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機師係最overpriced 嘅工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人工拉高曬啲票價 搞到廉航係咁加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又成日瞓過龍搞到delay<img src=\"/assets